rComments: Great prof, the more you put in the more you get out. He is really passionate about teaching and it makes going to class fun.  The textbook is like $300 and we barely used it, try to just share with other people in the class.

Bruno is the best prof I've ever had.  He goes above and beyond class.  Helped me figure out what I want to do with the rest of my life.  Super passionate...He is teaching because he wants to teach which is becoming more and more rare at U of T.  He is amazing.  Friend 4 Life.
Awesome! Nice guy, great teacher and really funny!

Takes forever to return papers.Marks your first paper properly and then every subsequent paper receives the same grade regardless of how much effort you put in to improve it. Disorganized. Presentations are never presented on assigned day (always delayed)
